onder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n河內去胡志明3X個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw好似未有人提seat61呢個網咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"真係北越玩到南越的話點都會停一停峴港，想去埋順化同會安 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nseat61一直有睇呀"},{"pid":"c570ff9d4caf8f4f6f2877afc01e336ae324aab3","tid":745664,"uid":56483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06effbe81de661d94766c006476fc0d302a8dba8","tid":745664,"uid":191312,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T21:12:07.000Z","msg":"啱啱坐完西伯利亞鐵路，真係挑戰人體極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:08:02.000Z","msg":"我個陣一日訓足12個鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 訓醒就食 食完就睇書寫日記 然後又再訓"},{"pid":"494a3eeed0d613ad8ac7a2212a0b579680fea2d4","tid":745664,"uid":15140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49dda131d48072f971d546d81d4f0326269d1c21","tid":745664,"uid":172694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T20:23:42.000Z","msg":"坐過86個鐘火車，坐到自己懷疑人生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b979c8aadf80817591d6ff8966e339f4e01aeb8a","tid":745664,"uid":191211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"中國火車旅行試過<br />\n<br />\n長沙 - 硬座 - 深圳<br />\n成都 - 軟臥 - 北京<br />\n承德 - 普速硬座 - 錫林浩特<br />\n錫林浩特 - 普速硬臥 - 二連<br />\n二連 - 硬座 - 呼和浩特<br />\n呼和浩特 - 硬座 - 包頭<br />\n包頭 - 硬臥 - 銀川<br />\n銀川 - 硬座 - 中衛<br />\n成都 - 硬臥 - 貴陽<br />\n貴陽 - 動車 - 廣州<br />\n石家莊 - 硬座 - 北京<br />\n北京 - 硬臥 - 香港<br />\n長沙 - 硬臥 - 廣州<br />\n<br />\n普速車冇冷氣，而且可以開窗，冇乜人坐嘅話其實好舒服。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n軟臥就真心訓得舒服，有房門，唔駛太擔心私隱同行李問題，不過比較貴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n硬臥 CP 值最高，叫做可以訓個覺休息，不過冇乜私隱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通宵硬座真係不了，好辛苦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce03e2994f5407d51c008f11e8bb6e10385d943","tid":745664,"uid":191211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2bec85bfab933dcb096d27a8c1867e6594b3576","tid":745664,"uid":161749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f79414eedbbb8ebbb476a1ea414223fcd36100a6","tid":745664,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"444f62a0a1bf34e58d5add873e4decf91c2cf571","tid":745664,"uid":161749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T03:36:50.000Z","msg":"分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 坐過一次紅磡北京上咗癮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T07:46:20.000Z","msg":"一直好想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會好辛苦？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:27:40.000Z","msg":"一開始覺得時間長，但其實冇咩問題<br />\n瞓醒第二日食個午餐已經到北京<br />\n有時間又可以同其他人交流吓<br />\n我覺得會多種旅行feel係飛機俾唔到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"香港北京直通車好少會爆<br />\n好鬆動，淡季可以幾卡都係吉車<br />\n而且多數都係遊客先會坐<br />\n所以氣氛幾好，好容易同人傾計交流<br />\n<br />\n而且車卡由於係去香港關係，會keep得比較新淨<br />\n唔似上面啲車卡，總係有陣up 味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2ff4c6b19154cc4b60fe79972123800691fd56","tid":745664,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:47:46.000Z","msg":"最癲一次係<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/114513_f190dba252b833a3bf63b6884eb92472.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F114513_f190dba252b833a3bf63b6884eb92472.jpeg&h=5504e4cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c1bf97456808dc725ae23a55936d0b70e47c81a","tid":745664,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite